'''拉斯坦'''（{{lang-ar|<big>الرستن</big>}}）是[[叙利亚|叙利亚]][[霍姆斯省|霍姆斯省]]的一个城市，位于[[霍姆斯_(敘利亞)|霍姆斯]]以北20公里，距离[[哈马|哈马]]22公里。居于叙利亚的中间地带，该地有建于[[奥龙特斯河|奥龙特斯河]]上的最古老的一座容纳2.25亿立方米的[[水坝|水坝]]<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.fao.org/|title= FAO.org|accessdate= 2007-07-19|language= |archive-date= 2012-07-11|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120711004347/http://www.fao.org/|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

在[[叙利亚内战|2011年叙利亚反政府衝突]]中，该地于2011年9月下旬受到政府部队的围攻<ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-13628776|title= BBC News - Syria: Attack on central town or Rastan 'kills 15'|accessdate= 2011-07-02|language= |date= 2011-06-02|archive-date= 2011-06-06|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110606083931/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-13628776|dead-url= no}}</ref>。9月27日，政府军在[[坦克|坦克]]和[[直升机|直升机]]的掩护下进攻当地的[[自由叙利亚军|自由叙利亚军]]。一名变节军官通过电话告诉[[半岛电视台|半岛电视台]]说，有400辆坦克开进了该地<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/09/201192772414155988.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-30 |archive-date=2011-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111030111059/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/09/201192772414155988.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。官方的[[SANA|SANA]]报道，在经过5天的激烈战斗后到了10月2日当地的生活已经恢复平静<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/16385-syria-trumpets-government-capture-of-rastan |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-30 |archive-date=2012-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120404084124/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/16385-syria-trumpets-government-capture-of-rastan |dead-url=no }}</ref>。一个名叫Rami Abdul-Rahman的活动家告诉记者，政府部队把自由军赶出了该地<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dp-news.com/en/detail.aspx?articleid=98524 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120405223643/http://www.dp-news.com/en/detail.aspx?articleid=98524 |archive-date=2012-04-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。至少27人在战斗中死亡<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/video/2011/10/06/crackdown-in-rastan-syria?videoId=222304800|work=Reuters|title=Crackdown in Rastan, Syria (1:16)|accessdate=2012-01-30|archive-date=2011-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111007203245/http://www.reuters.com/video/2011/10/06/crackdown-in-rastan-syria?videoId=222304800|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中7人是政府軍士兵和警察<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-15121876 | work=BBC News | title=Syria unrest: Heavy clashes erupt in Homs province | date=2011-09-30 | accessdate=2012-01-30 | archive-date=2011-12-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111208161048/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-15121876 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，10名是变节军<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/syria-security-forces-enter-rastan-as-army-defector-clashes-continue-1.387486 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-30 |archive-date=2012-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120103143735/http://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/syria-security-forces-enter-rastan-as-army-defector-clashes-continue-1.387486 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

反對派在2012年1月再次[[第二次拉斯坦战役|控制]]拉斯坦。<ref name="AJE1"/>

敍利亞政府於2018年5月16日在反對派轉移至伊德利卜省後，重新控制拉斯坦。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sana.sy/en/?p=137892|title=National flag hoisted over al-Rastan and Talbeisa|date=16 May 2018|publisher=[[Syrian_Arab_News_Agency|Syrian Arab News Agency]]|accessdate=2018-05-28|archive-date=2018-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180521154918/https://sana.sy/en/?p=137892|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-raises-flag-over-long-time-rebel-stronghold-in-northern-homs/|title=Syrian Army raises flag over long-time rebel stronghold in northern Homs|date=15 May 2018|publisher=[[Al_Masdar_News|Al Masdar News]]|accessdate=2018-05-28|archive-date=2018-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180515184000/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-raises-flag-over-long-time-rebel-stronghold-in-northern-homs/|dead-url=no}}</ref>


